## Credential Protocol ## {#sctn-credential-protocol}

Credential Protocol defines the ADIA-specific mechanisms with issuance, revocation & expiration of the Verifiable Credentials from the Issuer to the User. 
It also describes steps for Proof Presentation by a User to the Service Provider.

