### Implemented By
* Issuer Agent
* Cloud Agent
* Service Provider Agent

### Roles
* Issuer - Issues, Revokes & Expires VC & Stores the VC in VC Store
* User - Requests, Proposes, Receives the VC
* SP - Requests Proof Presentation to User

### States (if any)
```None```

### Sub/Co-protocols
This protocol uses following standard Aries/DIDComm protocols defined in Aries-RFCs -

* ```/didcomm.org/1.0/issue-credential``` - as a subprotocol to issue a VC

